name: QUALNET
description: QUALNET (QAN) is a pioneering Layer 1 blockchain engineered to provide a quantum-resistant foundation for the next generation of secure digital assets and decentralized applications. Leveraging a unique Proof-of-Quantum (PoQ) consensus mechanism and an integrated AI-driven optimization engine, QUALNET solves the critical security vulnerabilities inherent in classical elliptic curve cryptography. The network offers full EVM compatibility, allowing developers to deploy existing Ethereum-based dApps onto a future-proof, high-throughput environment. From securing Real-World Assets (RWA) to powering IoT solutions and decentralized AI, QUALNET serves as the essential security layer for a post-quantum digital economy.
